oop.library/OOP_RemSuperClass                   oop.library/OOP_RemSuperClass

    NAME
  OOP_RemSuperClass -- removes a superclass from a class' superclasslist

    SYNOPSIS
  error = OOP_RemSuperClass(class, superClass)
  D0                        A0     A1

  LONG OOP_RemSuperClass(APTR, APTR);

    FUNCTION
  This function will remove a superclass from the class' superclasslist. If
  the class has objects, the corresponding superclass objects will also be
  removed.

    INPUTS
  class -- class to remove superclass from.
  superClass -- the superclass to remove.

    RESULT
  OOPRCR_OK if all went ok, an errorcode otherwise.

    SEE ALSO
  OOP_AddSuperClass, oop.h

